                    <li>View IPv6 along with IPv4 address</li>
                    <li>Configure commands for non elementary OS distros</li>
                    <li>Fix a bug which prevented re-size of the disclaimer screen</li>
                    <li>Improve obtaining network details with use of ip command instead of the ifconfig one</li>
                </ul>
            </description>
